title: Bobby Set Himself on Fire! + Raymundo’s In-Law Controversy + What Country Artist Gave Russell Dickerson’s Baby Yeezy shoes
itunes:title: Bobby Set Himself on Fire! + Raymundo’s In-Law Controversy + What Country Artist Gave Russell Dickerson’s Baby Yeezy shoes
description:
Bobby talks about performing stunts over the weekend while shooting his NatGeo show. He talks about falling off a house and setting himself on fire! Eddie and Lunchbox bring controversy to the show about Raymundo moving into his in-law's property. We talk to Russell Dickerson about his new album, full circle Opry moment and the coolest baby gift a country artist gave him.
